    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presented for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a high-gloss shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel well, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the leather seats have been regularly conditioned. You will find minor creasing on the driver\u2019s seat consistent with standard use, but no tears or thinning. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It has a documented service history, including a recent oil service and a cooling system flush completed within the last 3,000 miles. The tires are matching sets with approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been a dependable daily driver and is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
